Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:35.49,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Sometimes I wonder again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:41.01,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}跨越数千年 接力棒传到我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:45.51,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因漫长道路而目眩 天旋地转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:51.26,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定有尚未发现的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:55.85,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}时刻都在这样思索 思索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:00.98,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不惧失败 反复尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:06.89,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哭着笑着 追寻光明
